'From Squeak3.7beta of ''1 April 2004'' [latest update: #5923] on 27 May 2004 at 1:57:18 pm'!"Change Set:		MultipleEmphDate:			27 May 2004Author:			Yoshiki OhshimaAn attempt to fix the handling of multiple text attributes."!!ParagraphEditor methodsFor: 'editing keys' stamp: 'yo 5/27/2004 13:56'!setEmphasis: emphasisSymbol	"Change the emphasis of the current selection."	| oldAttributes attribute |	oldAttributes _ paragraph text attributesAt: self selectionInterval first forStyle: paragraph textStyle.	attribute _ TextEmphasis perform: emphasisSymbol.	(emphasisSymbol == #normal) 		ifFalse:	[oldAttributes do:				[:att | (att dominates: attribute) ifTrue: [attribute turnOff]]].	self replaceSelectionWith: (self selection addAttribute: attribute)! !